pageProduct.name: Thompson's One-A-Day Bilberry 12000mg 60 Capsules
pageProduct.description:
General Information

Thompson's One-A-Day Bilberry 12000 supports healthy eyes and circulation

Thompson's One-A-Day Bilberry is suitable for:


  • Individuals who wish to support healthy eye function

  • Those who seek a rich source of antioxidants to maintain the health of their capillaries

Size: 60caps

KEY FEATURES

• Supports healthy eye function
• Supports blood capillary health
• Vegetarian/Vegan friendly
• One-A-Day Dose
• A rich source of antioxidants




Warnings

If symptoms persist consult your healthcare professional.

Ingredients

Active Ingredients: Each capsule contains: Herbal extract equiv. to fresh:
Vaccinium myrtillus (Bilberry) fruit 12g (12000mg)
equiv. Anthocyanosides 43mg

Directions

Store below 30°C in a dry place. Do not use if bottle and/or cap seal is missing or broken. Keep out of reach of children.

Storage Temperature: Below 30°C

Recyclable Packaging?: Yes
